actionConfiguration.body:
INSERT INTO pipeline_master 
SET
camera_id ={{Select1.selectedOptionValue}},
model_id ={{Select2.selectedOptionValue}},
processing_type ={{Select3.selectedOptionValue}},
skip_frames ={{Select4.selectedOptionValue}},
do_tracking ={{Checkbox1.isChecked?1:0}},
zone_flag ={{Checkbox2.isChecked?1:0}},
zone_topleft_x ={{Input3.text}},
zone_topleft_y ={{Input4.text}},
zone_botright_x ={{Input5.text}},
zone_botright_y ={{Input6.text}},
status = 'Inactive',
created_by = {{Text5.text}};
select last_insert_id() as last_insert_id;
